WES MOORE, Governor Ch. 547
Chapter 547
(House Bill 564)
AN ACT concerning
Business Regulation – Pet Cremation and Burial Services – Requirements
(Pet Cremation and Burial Services Consumer Protection Act)
FOR the purpose of establishing certain consumer protection requirements for registered
cemeterians, registered cemetery operators, or and certain permit holders and
licensees that sell or offer for sale pet cremation services of pet remains; establishing
the duties of certain persons responsible for returning pet cremains to certain animal
owners after cremation; and generally relating to the cremation of pet remains.
